               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     An undated <title>Dīvān</title> of the poems of Jāmī (d. 1492), possibly completed in <placeName ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7000231" key="place_7000231">Greater Iran</placeName> in the <date cert="medium" calendar="#Gregorian" notBefore="1750" notAfter="1850">late 18th to early 19th century</date>.
                     A note by the colophon attributes the hand to one <persName>Ghulām Ḥusayn Ḥasan Ḥusayn</persName>. 
                  </summary>
